asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Gnu-Metal-Guru-EC2BTX-Snowboard-2013/270915P,default,pd.html  Have you ever wondered if there is a snowboard out there that can do everything on the mountain with ease? Now there is with the GNU Metal Guru, this snowboard kills it in the all-mountain freestyle category. Starting with EC2 BTX riders enjoy the smooth sound of elliptical camber while raging to catch-free jibbing, out of this world control and lively pop. Banana between your feet for hardpack and ice carving and insane float in pow. Magnetraction creates positive edgehold in all condition and shines on ice. The GNU Metal Guru is a snowboard where you can throw on your tunes, crank up the volume, and the magic start happening.
